line_1: But o'er her child, forgetting all her pangs,
line_2: Insatiate of her smiles, the raptur'd parent hangs.

line_1: Can ye allay the dying parent's pangs,
line_2: When stern Oppression, in his harpy-fangs,

line_1: The gluttonous bird, exulting in his pangs,
line_2: Tears his swoln liver with remorseless fangs.
